{"tid":2227932,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"你個單位幾靚都冇用 鄰居質素先係最重要","createTime":"2020-10-03T07:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T14:14:12.000Z","uid":98473,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2e613ddc241bf64b390b1d7ea57f1c2002f98f75","tid":2227932,"uid":98473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:29:37.000Z","msg":"隔離屋係痴線佬<br />\n樓上個層係咁嘈<br />\n你間屋幾靚都冇用"},{"pid":"109beace20fd363ed31d5482207ad3ca8940403b","tid":2227932,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:32:32.000Z","msg":"隔離同樓下都係藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84857395b8737735595fbd29c848bb04f994efbb","tid":2227932,"uid":191815,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:32:49.000Z","msg":"台灣天王周杰倫向來是鋼琴高手，前日他在IG上載家中彈鋼琴的片段，只見他演奏時相當陶醉，留言說︰「深夜鋼琴，猜猜是哪首曲子。」有網民留言說︰「吵到鄰居了。」周董竟神回︰「我有想過，但我家沒鄰居，謝謝。」相當霸氣。<br />\n<br />\n原來周董身處的台北頂層複式豪宅「和平大苑」，是他在15年以1.7億港元購入，用作與太太昆凌的愛巢。豪宅有360度全景觀大露台，坐擁全台北景色，而且頂層複式單位為一層一伙，周董沒講大話，他的確沒有鄰居，所以即使半夜彈琴，也不怕吵醒他人。不少網民留言表示想做周董的鄰居，也有人說︰「<strong>哈哈，有錢煩惱，連鄰居都沒有。</strong>」"},{"pid":"2edf88d2977a9c88b3d2a18018793a1498440f4b","tid":2227932,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:40:42.000Z","msg":"有無人連鄰居姓乜同乜野樣都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcc8b6a1dfb23a1884b1d4b6b7bd2416901209fe","tid":2227932,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2edf88d2977a9c88b3d2a18018793a1498440f4b","tid":2227932,"uid":212168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T07:40:42.000Z","msg":"有無人連鄰居姓乜同乜野樣都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:38:53.000Z","msg":"同鄰居做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"236f557a75fea74698eab27f3971ba29b5b3f19f","tid":2227932,"uid":357591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T14:14:12.000Z","msg":"同意，<br />\n<br />\n公屋真係住左好多痴線佬同變態佬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}